task.summary: Have all the functionality in the tree view of a strategy working
Added teacher filtering on the class selection page.
fixed the class page so it uses URL templates

Eliminated the need for ClassStrategyMap and made sure all class-related tables have a FK to class_sc. Made deletes of strategies depend only on foreign key cascades rather than explicit delete operations in code.
Added a transaction around the addClassStrategy operation so that a failure during the creation will rollback all insertions.
Beginning of documentation by adding a docs folder.
